dct_title_s: Map of Yosemite Valley, Yosemite National Park, California, Mariposa County
dct_description_sm: Department of the Interior, U.S. Geological Survey ; E.M. Douglas, geographer.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by soundings.
Includes "Index map" and table of "Altitude of principal points."
On verso: "The story of the Yosemite Valley," by F.E. Matthes (with photos).
